        <mxCell id="dD1uLhPECOwK_6Fe8-Jx-12" parent="1" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fontFamily=Comic Sans MS;fontStyle=1" value="&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 17px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;u&gt;FUNCTIONAL REQUIREMENTS&lt;br&gt;&lt;/u&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 16px;&quot;&gt;1. Services emits metrics to platforms.&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 16px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;2. Query/visualize metrics on dashboard.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 16px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;3. Define alert rules with thresholds over time windows.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 16px;&quot;&gt;4. Receive notifications when alerts fire.&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="140" width="460" x="-620" y="350" as="geometry" />
